 The medals for the Beijing 2022 Winter Olympic Games were unveiled on Tuesday. In 100 days' time, athletes from all over the world will gather in Beijing and strive to achieve the ultimate honor of Olympic glory. What's behind a medal? Honor and dreams, sweat and tears. Over the past several months, Xinhua has followed some of the people who were closely connected to the medals' design and manufacturing processes. Click to find out the story behind the Olympic medals. Produced by Xinhua Global Service 